The '''Brooks-British Range tundra''' is an ecoregion spanning North America and Canada, and is one of the WWF Global 200 ecoregions
==References== {{Cite web |url=https://www.worldwildlife.org/ecoregions/na1108 |title=Brooks-British Range tundra |last1= Hagenstein |first1=R. |last2=Ricketts |first2=T. |access-date=2017-08-17 |website=World Wildlife Fund |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170903201724/https://www.worldwildlife.org/ecoregions/na1108 |archive-date=2017-09-03}}
