{{SIA|astronomical objects}}
{{Short pages monitor}}<!-- This long comment was added to the page to prevent it from being listed on Special:Shortpages. It and the accompanying monitoring template were generated via Template:Long comment. Please do not remove the monitor template without removing the comment as well.-->

{{redirect|Strangle the duck|the euphemistic meaning of the term|masturbation}}
'''Kots Kaal Pato''' ([[English language|English]]: '''Strangle the Duck''') is a controversial event practiced among some [[Mayan people|Mayan]] youth in the village of [[Izamal Municipality|Citilcum]] within the [[Administrative divisions of Mexico|Mexican state]] of [[Yucatán (state)|Yucatán]]. In the event, [[ducks]], bound to high wooden crossbeams by their feet, are [[Mutilation|mutilated]] in a ceremony-like atmosphere. It has attracted condemnation from [[animal rights]] activists in the region, with several Mexican environmental authorities filing an [[animal cruelty]] complaint on the matter.<ref>{{citenews|title=Mexican Environmental Authorities file complaint against duck-killing ceremony|publisher=''[[The Yucatan Times]]''|url=http://www.theyucatantimes.com/2015/05/mexican-environmental-authorities-file-complaint-against-duck-killing-ceremony/|date=May 21, 2015|accessdate=September 13, 2015}}</ref>
==See also== *[[Animal cruelty in Mexico]]
